#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:324
msgid ""
"The Pythagorean theorem states that in a right triangle, the square of the "
"hypotenuse (c) equals the sum of squares of the other two sides (a and b)."
msgstr ""
"Το Πυθαγόρειο θεώρημα δηλώνει ότι σε ένα ορθογώνιο τρίγωνο, το τετράγωνο της"
" υποτείνουσας (c) ισούται με το άθροισμα των τετραγώνων των άλλων δύο "
"πλευρών (α και β)."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:334
msgid "Find Hypotenuse (c)"
msgstr "Εύρεση υποτείνουσας (γ)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:334
msgid "c = √(a² + b²)"
msgstr "c = √(a² + b²)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:335
msgid "Find Side a"
msgstr "Βρείτε την πλευρά α"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:335
msgid "a = √(c² - b²)"
msgstr "a = √(c² - b²)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:336
msgid "Find Side b"
msgstr "Βρείτε την πλευρά β"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:336
msgid "b = √(c² - a²)"
msgstr "b = √(c² - a²)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:341
msgid "Key Points"
msgstr "Βασικά Σημεία"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:343
msgid ""
"The theorem only applies to right triangles (triangles with a 90° angle)"
msgstr "Το θεώρημα ισχύει μόνο για ορθογώνια τρίγωνα (τρίγωνα με γωνία 90°)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:344
msgid "The hypotenuse (c) is always the longest side"
msgstr "Η υποτείνουσα (γ) είναι πάντα η μεγαλύτερη πλευρά"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/pythagorean_theorem_calculator.html:345
