#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:301
msgid ""
"Calculate horsepower from torque and RPM using the formula: HP = (Torque × "
"RPM) / 5252. This is the most common calculation for engine power."
msgstr ""
"Calculate horsepower from torque and RPM using the formula: HP = (Torque × "
"RPM) / 5252. This is the most common calculation for engine power."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:305
msgid ""
"Calculate torque from horsepower and RPM. Formula: Torque = (HP × 5252) / "
"RPM. Useful for determining engine torque output."
msgstr ""
"Calculate torque from horsepower and RPM. Formula: Torque = (HP × 5252) / "
"RPM. Useful for determining engine torque output."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:309
msgid ""
"Calculate RPM from horsepower and torque. Formula: RPM = (HP × 5252) / "
"Torque. Useful for finding the RPM at which peak power occurs."
msgstr ""
"Calculate RPM from horsepower and torque. Formula: RPM = (HP × 5252) / "
"Torque. Useful for finding the RPM at which peak power occurs."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:313
msgid ""
"Convert between horsepower (HP), kilowatts (kW), and watts (W). Supports all"
" common power unit conversions."
msgstr ""
"Convert between horsepower (HP), kilowatts (kW), and watts (W). Supports all"
" common power unit conversions."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:317
msgid ""
"Calculate horsepower from watts. Formula: HP = Watts / 745.7. Useful for "
"converting electrical power to mechanical power."
msgstr ""
"Calculate horsepower from watts. Formula: HP = Watts / 745.7. Useful for "
"converting electrical power to mechanical power."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/horsepower_calculator.html:321
